Hey, I'm Kevin

I am a Full-Stack web developer with experience working in Python/Django, MERN, and C#/Asp.net

My Story:

After leaving my hometown of Las Vegas to join the Air Force, I began my life journey in Alaska working in transportation. I spent the next four years there with one deployment to Qatar. When my contract was over, I decided to continue my operations career in Seattle, WA. At the same time, I finished my Associate's degree in Transportation and my Bachelor's in Business/International finance.

My whole life, I loved working with computers, creating awesome things out of nothing, automating & organizing operations, and creating my own art. I realized that I wasn't getting enough of that in my field of work, and moving to Seattle helped me discover the world of computer programming. The Bellevue based school, Coding Dojo, has taught and prepared me to become a self-suficient, savvy, full-stack developer ready for anything thrown my way!
